    examTip: "Memorize the five steps of revenue recognition in order; knowing the sequence can help you eliminate incorrect answer choices quickly.",
    memoryAid: "I-PO-TA-R: Identify, Performance Obligations, Transaction Amount, Allocate, Recognize",
    reference: "ASC 606-10-25",
