    examTip: "Remember that 'proprietary' sounds like 'property,' and businesses own property, so proprietary funds use the same accounting as for-profit businesses.",
    memoryAid: "Proprietary = Property = Private Sector Accounting",
    reference: "GASB 34; GASB Codification §Sp20",
