      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Unrealized gains or losses on available-for-sale securities are recognized in OCI, not directly in net income, until the security is sold or impaired.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - There is no basis for using a midpoint value. The security must be reported at its fair value at the date of transfer.",
