      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Ineffectiveness in a fair value hedge is recognized immediately in net income; it is not deferred to accumulated other comprehensive income (AOCI).",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - While the inventory's carrying amount is adjusted to reflect the fair value change, the futures contract gain is not directly used to offset the carrying amount. Both amounts are recognized separately in net income.",
