      2: "Why option C is WRONG - The assessment period for going concern is one year, not two years, from the date the financial statements are issued or available to be issued.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - The assessment period is measured from the date the financial statements are issued or available to be issued, not three months from the reporting date.",
