    section: "FAR",
    blueprintArea: "FAR-III",
    topic: "Going Concern",
    subtopic: "Disclosure When Doubt is Alleviated",
    difficulty: "medium",
    skillLevel: "Application",
    question: "Under ASC 205-40, if management concludes that substantial doubt about the entity's ability to continue as a going concern is raised BUT alleviated by management's plans, the entity must:",
