      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Exchange rate movements, including a return to the original rate, do not trigger a reclassification of the CTA to net income; the CTA reflects the cumulative effect of all exchange rate changes over the investment's life.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - There is no threshold based on the CTA balance as a percentage of total equity that triggers a reclassification to net income; the reclassification is event-driven, not balance-driven.",
