    examTip: "Remember that fair value is king in business combinations; always look for the option that emphasizes fair value at the acquisition date when dealing with consideration transferred.",
    memoryAid: "FV-CAT: Fair Value of Consideration includes Assets, Transferred, Liabilities Incurred, and equity interests.",
    reference: "ASC 805-30-30-7",
