    examTip: "Focus on the substance over form when evaluating contracts under ASC 606; a handshake deal can be just as valid as a formal written agreement if all other criteria are met.",
    memoryAid: "Think of the acronym 'PICCC' (Probable, Identifiable, Commitment, Commercial, Collectible) to remember the key elements of a contract under ASC 606.",
