    examTip: "Remember that intraperiod tax allocation focuses on items reported below income from continuing operations and items affecting equity; think 'below the line' items.",
    memoryAid: "Think 'CODI': Continuing Operations, Discontinued Operations, Items charged directly to Equity, and Other comprehensive Income. These are the key areas for intraperiod tax allocation.",
