    educational: "Share-based compensation aims to align employee and shareholder interests. By using fair value at the grant date, companies accurately reflect the economic cost of these awards, providing a more transparent view of compensation expenses. This approach ensures that the financial statements reflect the true cost of attracting and retaining talent.",
