      2: "Why option C is WRONG - A two-year period is not the timeframe required by ASC 205-40 for going concern assessments; the standard focuses on the upcoming year.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - A five-year period is far beyond the scope of the going concern assessment required by ASC 205-40, which concentrates on the next twelve months.",
