    examTip: "Pay close attention to the timeframe specified in going concern questions; the 'one year after issuance' rule is frequently tested.",
    memoryAid: "Think 'Going Concern - One Year After Issuance' (GC-OYAI)",
    reference: "ASC 205-40-50-1",
