    options: ["The old TDR guidance continues to apply for debtors","ASC 470-50 modification vs. extinguishment guidance applies to all debt modifications, including those with borrowers experiencing financial difficulty","No accounting standard addresses debt modifications","ASC 842 lease modification guidance by analogy"],
