    educational: "Restricted Stock Units (RSUs) are a form of equity compensation. Under ASC 718, the compensation expense is based on the grant-date fair value of the RSUs, recognized over the service period (vesting period). Graded vesting allows for either straight-line or accelerated attribution methods for expense recognition.",
