      2: "Why option C is WRONG - While a segment's asset size is a factor, the threshold is 10% or more of the combined assets of all operating segments, not a fixed dollar amount.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - The number of employees is not a quantitative threshold used to determine reportable operating segments under ASC 280.",
