    educational: "Subsequent events are events occurring between the balance sheet date and the date the financial statements are issued or are available to be issued. Type I events relate to conditions that existed at the balance sheet date, requiring adjustments to the financial statements. Type II events relate to conditions that arose after the balance sheet date, and generally only require disclosure.",
