      2: "Why option C is CORRECT - An uncertain tax position (UTP) is recognized only if it is more-likely-than-not (greater than 50% probability) to be sustained on its technical merits. If this threshold is met, the benefit recognized is the largest amount that has a greater than 50% probability of being realized upon ultimate settlement.",
