    examTip: "Remember the acronym 'CARE' - Current rate for Assets, Revenues use average, Equity uses historical rates.",
    memoryAid: "Equity's roots are in the past; use the historical rate to keep it steadfast.",
    reference: "ASC 830-10-45",
