    educational: "Not-for-profit organizations receive many volunteer services, but only some are recognized as revenue. To be recognized, the services must either create or enhance a non-financial asset or require specialized skills, be provided by individuals possessing those skills, and would typically need to be purchased if not donated. This ensures only significant and measurable contributions are reflected in the financial statements.",
    examTip: "Focus on the keywords 'create/enhance non-financial asset' and 'specialized skills' when evaluating contributed services questions.",
    memoryAid: "Think 'CASE': Contributed services are recognized when they Create/enhance assets, or require Specialized skills, and would be Expected to be purchased otherwise.",
