    examTip: "Remember 'measurable and available' for derived tax revenues; think of it as 'transaction happened AND we can get the money soon'.",
    memoryAid: "DTA: Derived Tax Available - think 'Derived Tax revenues are recognized when they are Available.'",
    reference: "GASB 33",
